{"tid":1095860,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"支持政府開設以下牌照","createTime":"2019-04-07T10:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T10:24:59.000Z","uid":24390,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dde792105f6a1c886281512ce9e8121d1181224e","tid":1095860,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"香港廢老妹下妹下就係人都知<br />\n但係好多時啲廢青都好激氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我覺得以下日常生活嘅行為都要有牌先做得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擔遮：<br />\n擔縮骨遮要協返個縮骨遮牌，要有師傅係隔離儲夠30小時用縮骨遮仲要中途唔可以犯錯<br />\n例如：對人開遮/行街轉遮有細剔，有兩個細tick就fail,要兩年後重考，中途淨係可以着雨褸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n血的子/插眼就馬上fail,終身冇得retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長遮要有縮骨遮牌一年先考得，準則同縮骨遮差唔多，但係fail咗就立即釘埋縮骨遮牌<br />\n<br />\n行路：<br />\n冇考到每次出街唔可以超過30mins<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準則參考車牌，打燈讓路cut線etc, 甩p先可以邊行邊聽歌/玩電話<br />\n<br />\n用atm:<br />\n開acc果時要考埋牌，用atm時間<br />\n超過2mins就唔畀開acc<br />\n1-2mins就可以開basic acc<br />\n30s以下會自動送$500 reward<br />\n如果發現有牌但係磨多過2mins就將個acc充公<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗到再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34ab31eb7eea55df9ae0ec59f39727f922f4d02","tid":1095860,"uid":63864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"開post要攞牌"},{"pid":"e69ed983e393636be5837da640dcb956f4552118","tid":1095860,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e34ab31eb7eea55df9ae0ec59f39727f922f4d02","tid":1095860,"uid":63864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"開post要攞牌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:24:59.000Z","msg":"畀啲準則嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}